processFileData:
RSCSVR66_SFG PROCESS

        SNODE=SFGDEV

        &INFILE="%FA_FILE_FOUND"

        &FILENAME="%FA_NOT_PATH"
		&TRXMODE=binary
CDCP COPY

    FROM (

        FILE="&INFILE"
		sysopts=":datatype=&TRXMODE:"
        PNODE

)

ckpt = 2M

    TO (

        FILE = "/mailbox/STDCWHSE/RSCSVR66/&FILENAME"
		sysopts=":datatype=&TRXMODE:"
        SNODE

        DISP=RPL

                )
IF (CDCP EQ 0) THEN
ACK RUN TASK PNODE (PGM=UNIX)
SYSOPTS="rm &INFILE"
EIF


PEND
